description	"Imperial Scout Trooper

Class: Clone Trooper.
Class Summary:
A lightly armored but versatile class capable of sniping, melee, and even defending against blaster fire.

Default Weaponry:
- Electro-Weapon * 

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Electro-Weapon
- Defense (1)
- Stun Baton and Shield can use dual style
- Can block lightsabers with Melee/Blaster Defense
- Can block blaster shots Melee/Blaster Defense
- Half damage compared to lightsaber

Inventory:
- Bacta (25+ HP)

Default Abilities:
- Assemble
- Dash (1)

Scout troopers are specialized stormtrooper variants used on a range of missions in containing and defusing insurrectionist scenarios due to the spread of the influence of the Rebel Alliance to even within loyalist populations in the Galactic Empire."